<br>
I would much rather pets got fixed somehow, so that we can use them on ANY raid, but VI's atttitude lately...*grimaces*<br>
We've already pointed out making pets neutral would mean no AFk XPing is possible which should please VI, as well as help us.<br>
<br>
Don't know if you've been to TOV or upper islands of Sky, but they are prime examples of where pets are totally FUBARed. isle 7 has pathing that's just totally &amp;$^$£%!<br>
<br>
Want mana galore? get a 56+ mage, slap a hit point buff (aegolism etc) and regen on him, assign a healer to look after  said mage, he casts Rod of Mystic Transvergance, uses 1 charge, drop rod now with 2 charges..he gets healed as needed. This system=mana GALORE <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Wizzie with epic hsould have rod hot keyed, runs low..click, loses no hit points thanks to epic rune (wonder if Spell shield works in conjunction with this, hm??), and gains 220 mana per click.<br>
<br>
you are correct, mages shouldn't get much increase in our DDs damage, unless ALL casters got an across the board % increase, not really sure thats needed though, more FT items from non-uber mobs seems better in regards to all Int caster balance problems? Would like to point out that our nukes and pets dont' scale after 50, which is one of the big bones of contention. <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> <br>
lvl 44nuke = 600 hp, lvl 44 pets hits for 48.<br>
Lvl 57 nuke hits for 825 hp, lvl 57 earth pet hits for 60<br>
</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
That doesn't scale well does it? I dont know if wizards have a similar problem in regards of scaling up 40 to post 50.<br>
And I know some wizzies will point out lvl 34 nukes here, ahem ours is a bolt and I personally have no objection to wizzies getting upgrades, I'm all for it! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
<br>
On a point I made: Do you think wizards should get more lures/banes at various levels? To me it would seem an excellent way to address some wiz problems, and make the game more fun (rather than camp the FBSS for a melee, camp the archmage for a Froglock Bane, hehe)<br>
<br>
Your idea of summoned arows is good, would like to see that myself, say it procs a lvl 8 nuke or some such, hehe <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
<br>
Anyway, I don't see wizards as rivals per se, but as colleagues: you do it one way, we do it another, hence I was asking your opinion <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Redorious<br>
Archmage<br>
